    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This kit can be used to clean and polish armor. Creatures wearing armor that has been maintained by this kit gain a +1 circumstance bonus on Diplomacy checks to Make an Impression on soldiers, guards, Gorumites, and other martially minded characters. This bonus expires after 24 hours, or if the armor is soiled in some way, such as by walking through a sewer or falling in a mud pit.",
